metadata.name: Loisaida 1/1
metadata.description:
Anchored to a complex past, a neighborhood embeds ambiguous heritage with venerable accents. An underground extension of deep influences. Self expressed ensembles evoke rainbowic tones. Ruby reds, feverish azures, saturated rouges, filigree gold embroidery. Solid over the knee socks trimmed by large buttoned coats, funky mini dresses and old shirts revamped. 

Synth Graph: a center front view portrait, 2012, photograph of three beautiful tanned female model best friends with blue hair, wearing intricately embroidered oversized street wear red coats with buttons and short blue skirts with black printed stockings, walking down the lower east side in the 2000s in early autumn at midnight, highly detailed. Sampler: klms, steps: 85, scale: 11.
